<h1 id="mission">Mission</h1>

<h2>
We aim to make MicroBlocks the most intuitive, fun, and engaging tool
for physical computing imaginable, and to create a global community
of learners and educators around it.
</h2>

<strong>
<ul>
	<li><p><span>
	• Help students and curious/creative makers everywhere
	discover the joys of physical computing.
	</span></p></li>
	<li><p><span>
	• Enable educators to create engaging, high-quality STEM/STEAM learning experiences.
	</li>
	<li><p><span>
	• Inspire a wide range of learners, especially those who do not initially
	see themselves as potential technologists.
	</span></p></li>
	<li><p><span>
	• Support hands-on learning and creative problem-solving.
	</span></p></li>
</ul>
</strong>
